No. 09-1186. John Errol Ferguson, et al., Petitioners v. Walter A. McNeil, Secretary, Florida Department of Corrections. 560 U.S. 949, 130 S. Ct. 3360,

176 L. Ed. 2d 1263,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4483. June 1, 2010.

Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 580 F.3d 1183.
